Package com.composum.pages.commons.model

Class SiteRelease

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.composum.pages.commons.model.AbstractModel
      • com.composum.pages.commons.model.SiteRelease
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Model, com.composum.sling.core.SlingBean, Comparable<SiteRelease>
    public class SiteRelease
extends AbstractModel
implements Comparable<SiteRelease>
    Models a release for a site. The actual resource is the metadata node of the release, which is located below "/var/composum", e.g. /var/composum/content/ist/composum/cpl:releases/r1.0/metaData .
